sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Knative Ingress Gateway<br/>(Istio)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant QueueProxy as Knative Activator /<br/>Queue Proxy<br/>8012/TCP
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as TGIS<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as OpenShift UWM<br/>(Prometheus)

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.3 (wildcard cert)
    Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012 / mTLS (Istio)
    QueueProxy->>Caikit: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080 / mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Generate text<br/>gRPC/8033 / plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS->>TGIS: GPU inference execution
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generation result
    Caikit-->>QueueProxy: JSON response
    QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: caikit.runtime.Nlp RPC<br/>HTTPS (h2) / TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012 / mTLS (Istio)
    QueueProxy->>Caikit: Inference request<br/>gRPC/8085 (h2c) / mTLS (sidecar)
    Caikit->>TGIS: Generate text<br/>gRPC/8033 / plaintext (localhost)
    TGIS->>TGIS: GPU inference execution
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Generation result
    Caikit-->>QueueProxy: gRPC response
    QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation (HTTP)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>QueueProxy: Forward<br/>mTLS
    QueueProxy->>Caikit: Streaming request<br/>HTTP/8080 / mTLS
    Caikit->>TGIS: Streaming generate<br/>gRPC/8033 / localhost
    loop Token streaming
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Token chunk
        Caikit-->>QueueProxy: SSE chunk
        QueueProxy-->>Gateway: Forward chunk
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk
    end

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 / PERMISSIVE mTLS<br/>(plaintext allowed)
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics

    Note over S3,TGIS: Flow 5: Model Loading (Init)

    S3-->>TGIS: Model artifacts download<br/>HTTPS/443 / TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Access Key
